{"tid":518431,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"[年經]賭大細數學一問","createTime":"2018-01-03T10:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-03T14:09:27.000Z","uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"81825ec3d14690d56fcfd6ff13fc0858efdff816","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"根據大數原理﹐如果賭大細局數愈多，開出黎大同細既次數(唔計圍骰)應該愈趨同。但同時，每局大細都係獨立事件，之前開得多大同之後開細既機率完全無關。<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢兩個理論係咪有衝突？定係我concept唔清？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"280d5df2b1a3ae684e4a40abd21f75e9568dea3c","tid":518431,"uid":157153,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:15:24.000Z","msg":"無衝突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n完"},{"pid":"0323452446ea1c3f1d8c0e06ef11700ae235cf65","tid":518431,"uid":76020,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:19:52.000Z","msg":"P(連續100 次大）<br />\nP(下一次係大）<br />\n<br />\n兩個唔同event 黎<br />\n<br />\n利申：讀文科"},{"pid":"2548dddebae3cddcfe264a734d8667258fbde2a4","tid":518431,"uid":57346,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"81825ec3d14690d56fcfd6ff13fc0858efdff816","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:13:49.000Z","msg":"根據大數原理﹐如果賭大細局數愈多，開出黎大同細既次數(唔計圍骰)應該愈趨同。但同時，每局大細都係獨立事件，之前開得多大同之後開細既機率完全無關。<br />\n<br />\n究竟呢兩個理論係咪有衝突？定係我concept唔清？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:23:16.000Z","msg":"機率不變所以每鋪無關係，機率不變所以越趨相同，唔只冇衝突，仲係主因！"},{"pid":"53bbe4eac9fffaef0d12fc46f7ce9024e543f6cd","tid":518431,"uid":73241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"一係咁講<br />\n你連續開左一萬鋪細<br />\n但係下一鋪依然都只會係五十五十<br />\n唔會自動修正overall個機率<br />\n而大數法則仍然適用<br />\n因為一萬鋪相比起無限(趨近)都只係好少"},{"pid":"d854989b0cb8c291f6b48487ce0a07fa35a70e7a","tid":518431,"uid":132847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:27:52.000Z","msg":"law of large number"},{"pid":"f4734db575e8cd95168aef55254d6a3c57d44573","tid":518431,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"衝突位喺邊？"},{"pid":"a9d1efe9235727bac19aa36d7f769b8a27fe4237","tid":518431,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:35:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/03/183347_e4c3cf1cd45b245874caa354715cba8d.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F03%2F183347_e4c3cf1cd45b245874caa354715cba8d.png&h=3f86a8f4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第二行去第三行assume 咗每個X係independent 所以先可以將variance of sum 變成 sum of variance 呢到反映出independency應該係law of large number 嘅前提"},{"pid":"1217f5ee4ae7e549ea812b074af7b7cefd2aa5a5","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4734db575e8cd95168aef55254d6a3c57d44573","tid":518431,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"衝突位喺邊？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"啲賭仔成日見到連續出左幾舖大，就落手買細，並以大數原理作辯護。但又有人話每舖係獨立事件，所以之前開得多大，對後面係咪開細無影響。"},{"pid":"230a3691ca82b0d3b672340951d881772c9a3f28","tid":518431,"uid":132847,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"1217f5ee4ae7e549ea812b074af7b7cefd2aa5a5","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4734db575e8cd95168aef55254d6a3c57d44573","tid":518431,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"衝突位喺邊？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"啲賭仔成日見到連續出左幾舖大，就落手買細，並以大數原理作辯護。但又有人話每舖係獨立事件，所以之前開得多大，對後面係咪開細無影響。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:38:50.000Z","msg":"呢個係 Hot hand fallacy <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"babe0cea8622d3690ca2ee7741804c6b559fdd71","tid":518431,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d333aa9f9a98c3c6a1e1f321bb2a3f61cc3f4378","tid":518431,"uid":113074,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"如果你個數夠大<br />\n會變咗做50 50％<br />\n咁你下一局會買大定細呢？<br />\n<br />\n如果你個數唔夠大<br />\n70 30％<br />\n咁又點會做大數呢？"},{"pid":"75dbc8c43e188b3737f5623e6b1fc0949f5517ac","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53bbe4eac9fffaef0d12fc46f7ce9024e543f6cd","tid":518431,"uid":73241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"一係咁講<br />\n你連續開左一萬鋪細<br />\n但係下一鋪依然都只會係五十五十<br />\n唔會自動修正overall個機率<br />\n而大數法則仍然適用<br />\n因為一萬鋪相比起無限(趨近)都只係好少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"所以大數原理淨係喺無限或者接近無限既背景下先有意義？<br />\n<br />\n咁我可唔可以話100舖大細下，開出大同細既次數，&ldquo;有更高可能&rdquo;會比喺10舖大細下更趨同？"},{"pid":"5541e6f38831c952d9a942b762aafda23f280f14","tid":518431,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:40:43.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1eb77ab50e63ff8c65bb6aa743592be18e901201","tid":518431,"uid":132847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"75dbc8c43e188b3737f5623e6b1fc0949f5517ac","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"53bbe4eac9fffaef0d12fc46f7ce9024e543f6cd","tid":518431,"uid":73241,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:27:22.000Z","msg":"一係咁講<br />\n你連續開左一萬鋪細<br />\n但係下一鋪依然都只會係五十五十<br />\n唔會自動修正overall個機率<br />\n而大數法則仍然適用<br />\n因為一萬鋪相比起無限(趨近)都只係好少"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:39:28.000Z","msg":"所以大數原理淨係喺無限或者接近無限既背景下先有意義？<br />\n<br />\n咁我可唔可以話100舖大細下，開出大同細既次數，&ldquo;有更高可能&rdquo;會比喺10舖大細下更趨同？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:42:27.000Z","msg":"同意<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7d997ea1584f1f2a7e263306fd530764e85d310","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"babe0cea8622d3690ca2ee7741804c6b559fdd71","tid":518431,"uid":77484,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:38:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:43:08.000Z","msg":"咁所以啲賭仔並非完全無道理，只係佢地既sample size太細，效果唔明顯？"},{"pid":"a6cf07e8b24b856b16dbfa4a994955b8c130d72f","tid":518431,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1217f5ee4ae7e549ea812b074af7b7cefd2aa5a5","tid":518431,"uid":164920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4734db575e8cd95168aef55254d6a3c57d44573","tid":518431,"uid":34301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:30:40.000Z","msg":"衝突位喺邊？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T10:36:56.000Z","msg":"啲賭仔成日見到連續出左幾舖大，就落手買細，並以大數原理作辯護。但又有人話每舖係獨立事件，所以之前開得多大，對後面係咪開細無影響。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T12:15:06.000Z","msg":"有冇衝突就要睇情況<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n「每舖係獨立事件」係我哋嘅假設，如果我哋跟住呢個假設去賭，咁呢類賭仔嘅講法先同假設有衝突啦<br />\n問題就係我哋唔肯定現實生活裡面每一局係咪真係獨立事件，所以其實你可以先做一啲test睇下每一個係咪獨立事件再判斷賭仔嘅講法係咪唔合理"},{"pid":"0a5fb3e63241a7cd1f2acd5efea0ffc91b2111da","tid":518431,"uid":100760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T14:09:27.000Z","msg":"大數定律係要&infin;咁多鋪大細<br />\n你賭到死嗰日都賭唔到&infin;鋪大細啦<br />\n唔係咩叫&infin;呀"}]}